sentences: The JWG met in a night session to adopt its organization of work and hear an oral report of the informal exchange of views and information on compliance at an event held on October 6 - 7 1999 in Vienna.
It then considered elements of the design, coverage and functions of a compliance system under the Protocol.
The JWG will reconvene on 29 October at 10:00 am.
enb_long_title: Fifth Conference of the Parties to the UN Framework Convention on Climate Change
